        <updateDate>2018-03-16T15:03:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Pretrial Integrity and Safety Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 to require the Department of Justice's Office of Justice Programs to make grants: (1) to replace bail systems that use payment of money as a condition of pretrial release in criminal cases, and (2) to implement a National Pretrial Reporting Program to collect data on the processing of defendants by state and local courts.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Pretrial Integrity and Safety Act of 2017</title>
