      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To provide grants to States and Indian tribes to reform their criminal justice system to encourage the replacement of the use of payment of secured money bail as a condition of pretrial release in criminal cases, and for other purposes.</title>
